'''BmKAEP''' (or anti-epilepsy peptide) is a [[neurotoxin]] from the [[venom]] of the [[Mesobuthus martensii|Manchurian scorpion]] ''(Mesobuthus martensii)''. It is a  β-toxin, which shift the activation voltage of sodium channels towards more negative potentials.

