== Therapeutic use ==
Though the exact mechanism of its anti-epilepsy effect is not clear, several studies have shown that BmKAEP can inhibit [[coriaria]] [[lactone]]-induced [[epilepsy]] in rats by prolonging the latent epilepsy period, relieving the degree of [[Epileptic seizure|seizures]] and shortening its average duration, at a pharmacological dosage of only 0,057&nbsp;µg/g.<ref name="eight article"/> 

''Mesobuthus martensii'', especially its tail, has been used in [[Chinese traditional medicine]] to treat several neuronal diseases, such as several types of [[paralysis]], [[apoplexy]] and epilepsy.<ref name="first article"/>

